Data Analyst Assignment:

Objective
This project demonstrates core data analysis skills using SQL, Spreadsheets, and Python. It includes database creation, data analysis, and basic programming tasks.
🛠️ Tools Used
SQL: MySQL Workbench
Spreadsheets: Microsoft Excel / Google Sheets
Programming: Python (VS Code)

