SQL Tasks:
Hotel Management System
Created tables: users, bookings, items, booking_commercials
Inserted sample data
Queries:
Last booked room per user
Total billing in November 2021
Bills greater than 1000
Most/least ordered items
Second highest bill
Clinic Management System
Created tables: clinics, customer, clinic_sales, expenses
Inserted sample data
Queries:
Revenue by sales channel
Top customers
Monthly profit/loss
Most profitable clinic
Second least profitable clinic


📊 Spreadsheet Tasks:
Created two sheets: ticket and feedbacks
Used XLOOKUP to fetch ticket created date
Created helper columns:
Same Day comparison using INT()
Same Hour comparison using HOUR()
Used COUNTIFS / Pivot Table for analysis



Python Tasks
1. Time Converter
Converts minutes into hours and minutes
Used integer division and modulus
2. Remove Duplicates
Removes duplicate characters from a string
Implemented using loop and condition


✅ Conclusion
This assignment covers:
SQL for database design and querying
Excel for data analysis and reporting
Python for basic programming logic